{"tid":1534762,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"FB 近排勁多譚姓歌手假廣告","createTime":"2019-09-03T06:07:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T04:09:59.000Z","uid":134993,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ad25e0f896d7d7be5d2c1dba473d42352974b0d3","tid":1534762,"uid":134993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:07:53.000Z","msg":"大家有無？"},{"pid":"26e3fb319758a455f19bb1bfec05f8439a6b5aeb","tid":1534762,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:08:02.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"857321e87a6fcfb01e296e6218ca3f28db91dd7a","tid":1534762,"uid":134993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad25e0f896d7d7be5d2c1dba473d42352974b0d3","tid":1534762,"uid":134993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:07:53.000Z","msg":"大家有無？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:10:01.000Z","msg":"關於投資<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c761d3c7198f5a499a0da7ae35e658466e539a2","tid":1534762,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:12:27.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"189be068675ef02bee75003dcb6e6279b5bcc393","tid":1534762,"uid":4174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:36:19.000Z","msg":"痴線 block 極都有"},{"pid":"8c532e53cb59c175430e55cbe187e94f998ab324","tid":1534762,"uid":316803,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:38:17.000Z","msg":"Facebook 會接照使用者瀏覽記錄落廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓主like過藍絲page?"},{"pid":"d387c37dae8880fdf308c1c4f0ce6a4005e0f84e","tid":1534762,"uid":134993,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8c532e53cb59c175430e55cbe187e94f998ab324","tid":1534762,"uid":316